{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/logo_en.png?t=1737513789\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Escape from the Cursed Convent&quot;</strong> is a narrative adventure game set in a medieval convent and it is a non official fan derivative work of the manga &quot;Hengoku no Schwester.&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title01_en.png?t=1737513789\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/library_hero_image.png?t=1737513789\" />Step into the 16th-century Holy Roman Empire through the eyes of Adeline, a young peasant girl whose mother is falsely accused of witchcraft. Adeline is sent to the Claustrum Convent for &quot;re-education&quot; where she faces a living hell of torment and executions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over the course of three to five hours, explore the convent\u2019s dark world featuring subtle elements of gore and yuri. Determined to escape, Adeline and her friend Helena embark on a daring journey driven by themes of saintliness, freedom, and faith.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title02_en.png?t=1737513789\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title02_img.png?t=1737513789\" />Step into a mesmerizing pixel art world rich with authentic medieval religious details. Explore the beautifully crafted convent accompanied by period-specific music and a cast of intriguing characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title03_en.png?t=1737513789\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title03_img.png?t=1737513789\" />Embark on an adventure spanning 3 to 5 hours where your choices influence the narrative. Experience multiple endings and side stories as you navigate the convent's mysteries. Form deep, perhaps unexpected connections with your companions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title04_en.png?t=1737513789\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/title04_img.png?t=1737513789\" />Enhance your journey with a variety of mini-games. Engage in Quick Time Events, test your skills in hunting, perfect your cooking, and discover many more activities as you explore the world with your protagonists.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Start Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1142740/482807f992615e74c213a1d1d5177f51772d3a54.jpg"},{"name":"Prologue","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1142740/8f0d74564d100c7cd8bed78658e71275190f58b9.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1142740/6393a58fcba489f50fba63a15a8584df35887865.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Two","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1142740/1197a828f9292b074091bdab10598c8476ad6e1b.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Three","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1142740/f2ced1fd8fc157bd97aeb7ba4edc3e1983244acd.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Four","path":